|Shestakov was whisked away from a penal colony on a [[Mil Mi-2|Mi-2]] helicopter hijacked by his accomplices, and re-captured shortly after his escape.<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/russia/9160388/Murderer-escapes-from-prison-by-helicopter.html | location=London | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Tom | last=Parfitt | title=Murderer escapes from prison by helicopter | date=March 22, 2012}}</ref>

